QuestData.Title: It's Treason, Then
QuestData.Description:
We've halted their efforts, but we still have more to do.
Sin'dane must have sent someone to oversee the encampment.
Find and slay whoever is in charge. Only then can we be sure their work has ended.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: The hand of Sin'dane in Revendreth--and a baroness hopeful.
QuestData.RewardText:
The Banished One... The Pauldrons of Imperium...
This lich, Kel'Thuzad, meddles with powerful forces.
